I would simply ask all of us to ask the Lord to reveal anything you're holding back and to help you surrender

00:46:13.314 --> 00:46:20.090
to him, to open your heart and let him fill you with his peace, his strength and his direction.

00:46:23.297 --> 00:46:28.830
Let's make this a moment of recommitment to walk humbly with our God.

00:46:31.396 --> 00:46:32.338
The altars are open.
